USERS
- username
- total upvotes that includes links and comment upvotes
- date creation

UPVOTES: USER/LINKS/COMMENTS Upvotes JOIN

FAVORITES: USER/LINKS JOIN
- linkID
- username (who has favorited link)

LINKS
- linkID
- url
- upvotes
- userID

Links(One) to Comments(many)

COMMENTS
- commentID
- linkID (as a foreign key)
- userID (as a foreign key)
- date creation
- commentUpvotes

NESTED COMMENTS: Parent Comment/Child Comment JOIN
- parentCommentID
- childCommentID
